sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant Main as C++ CLI
    participant Engine as Session Engine
    participant System as Linux OS
    
    Admin->>Main: vanish start privacy
    Main->>Engine: Initiate start request
    Engine->>System: useradd -m vanish_random
    Engine->>System: Initialize local IP tables rules
    Engine->>System: mount -t tmpfs (Privacy mode)
    Engine-->>Admin: Session Active
    
    note over Engine,System: Watcher Daemon monitors session state implicitly.
    
    Admin->>Main: vanish stop
    Main->>Engine: Initiate stop request
    Engine->>System: loginctl terminate-user
    Engine->>System: pkill -9 -u vanish_random
    Engine->>System: umount -l home_dir
    Engine->>System: userdel -r vanish_random
    Engine-->>Admin: Session Destroyed Thoroughly
